#

Herb-Crusted Pork Tenderloin with Garlic Butter Sauce

$25
600 kcal

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

PorkGourmetFrench CuisineDinner

Description

Succulent pork tenderloin, perfectly herb-crusted and drizzled with a rich garlic butter sauce for a gourmet experience.

Ingredients

  • Pork tenderloin: 1.5 lbs
  • Fresh thyme: 2 tbsp
  • Fresh rosemary: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic cloves: 6, minced
  • Unsalted butter: 1/2 cup
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Lemon juice: 1 tbsp
